I'd like to say.

1134
01:01:35.262 --> 01:01:37.231
<i>Chopped wood logs.</i>
<i>Chopped wood logs.</i>

1135
01:01:37.298 --> 01:01:38.265
<i>Lizard. Lizard.</i>

1136
01:01:39.266 --> 01:01:39.333
