1138
01:01:41.435 --> 01:01:43.003
<i>Potato. Potato. Loaf of bread.</i>
<i>Men wrestling. Loaf of bread.</i>

1139
01:01:43.070 --> 01:01:43.871
<i>Coconut. Hospital.</i>

1140
01:01:43.938 --> 01:01:45.806
-Okay. Enough.
- <i>Potato. Potato.</i>

1141
01:01:50.077 --> 01:01:51.745
