1164
01:03:34.549 --> 01:03:36.950
Could you just. um.
scooch back a little?

1165
01:03:37.017 --> 01:03:38.319
Yeah. Oh. Perfect.

1166
01:03:38.385 --> 01:03:40.020
Yep. that's him.

1167
01:03:40.087 --> 01:03:41.221
All right. everyone.

1168
01:03:41.288 --> 01:03:44.024
