1172
01:03:48.495 --> 01:03:50.064
Be back in a minute.

1173
01:03:53.000 --> 01:03:55.369
Mabel. what's going on?
What did you do?

1174
01:03:55.436 --> 01:03:57.304
Where'd it go? Did it leave?

1175
01:04:02.443 --> 01:04:03.477
