-Mabel.

1193
01:05:20.454 --> 01:05:21.455
Huh?

1194
01:05:21.523 --> 01:05:22.389
-Hey.
-Hey.

1195
01:05:22.456 --> 01:05:23.323
Oh. hey.

1196
