1229
01:07:01.455 --> 01:07:02.422
Okay. Mabel. I don't know
why you're a beaver now.

1230
01:07:03.190 --> 01:07:03.257
It's okay.
We can work this out.

1231
01:07:04.324 --> 01:07:04.391
Just stay the course.

1232
01:07:05.392 --> 01:07:05.459
